== See Also ==
* {{ill|Endemic disease (Japanese schistosomiasis)|ja|地方病 (日本住血吸虫症)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Endemic disease (Japanese schistosomiasis)|1=local disease|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11086612}}: The Kofu Basin was the largest region in Japan affected by {{ill|schistosomiasis|ja|日本住血吸虫症|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/schistosomiasis|1=schistosomiasis japonica|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q56351164}}, but efforts by researchers and physicians led to its eradication, declared in 1996. The shift from rice cultivation to fruit farming since the 1960s was partially motivated by disease control efforts.

